                     <interp inst="t18531212-147-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>, stealing 1 pair of boots, 2 waistcoats, 1 gown, and other articles, value 9<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 18<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18531212-name-141" type="victimName">
