                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I can positively swear that the prisoner is the man I saw on the stairs—there is an inner door with a bell to it, and he must have watched the news boy in with the paper when the servant admitted him, and got in at that time—the inner door was open when I saw him, and the outer door was always open except at night.</p>
